channel.title: [Turbo] Blue's Damn GI Turbo D5 (The Mastermeme, The Robber, and Meathead win)
channel.description:
# Grand Idea Turbo
* Days are 15 minutes. Nights are 5 minutes. Twilight is however long it takes. * Logs do ***not*** exist. * Lynches are majority only. * Trials exist. * There can be more than one King, but only a King election will take place once there are no Kings remaining. * I’m on a laptop atm. * The amount of players are infinite but there must be at least 7 players. * Classes will be at least 50% BD/Uninformed Majority-siding.
Players: 1. Isaac_Gonzalez - Alive 2. DatBird - Alive 3. WazzaAzza - Drunk (Dead D1) 5. GamerPoke - Order FK (Dead N3) 6. Simon - Fan Favourite (Dead D2) 7. Firekitten - Robber (Dead D3) 4. eevee (mid dle) - Psycho King (Dead D4) 8. Soulshade55r - Reinhardt (Dead D3) 9. Margaret - Alive 10. Geyde - Town Arborist (Dead D1) 11. PoisonedSquid - Alive 12. Mercenary - CASTOR (Lynched D2) 13. MaximusPrime - POLLUX (Modkilled D3) 14. Livicus - Damon Gant (Dead D4) # Classes will be rolled up until 1491.
